{"tid":1076390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到隔離post恥笑英國，我覺得好可笑","createTime":"2019-03-24T21:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T01:27:00.000Z","uid":54344,"like":13,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8c8c7f2d22f35c44daa9ae67b8d81ac76ae0dd","tid":1076390,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T21:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwFXH1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwFXH1c.jpg&h=710b0143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果英國人宜家先醒覺，認為留返喺歐盟先係正確的話，用主流人民嘅意願去決定國家前途，點解唔係咁先係真正彰顯民主咩？<br />\n<br />\n係，你可以話佢地彈出彈入，until we score。但如果大多數人，或者主流意見覺得都有需要公投的話，舉行公投又有咩問題呢？<br />\n<br />\n當真係搞唔成公投，十年二十年後，唔通又話想公投重返歐盟，你又話人地出爾反爾？"},{"pid":"d3e9a0cfe84da8850046dcd9eb12153744305a02","tid":1076390,"uid":20414,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T21:06:49.000Z","msg":"大多數人？主流意見？<br />\nHow to define mainstream? <br />\n沉默既人投左票唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb65f861d11f8133a127085568506fad4a802c4","tid":1076390,"uid":54344,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"d3e9a0cfe84da8850046dcd9eb12153744305a02","tid":1076390,"uid":20414,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T21:06:49.000Z","msg":"大多數人？主流意見？<br />\nHow to define mainstream? <br />\n沉默既人投左票唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T21:09:12.000Z","msg":"當然我唔係英國人我唔知啦，講緊如果。當然假設性問題我地解答唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315bee0c8914871a94fc3695c3d72e0d8ff6d270","tid":1076390,"uid":234658,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T21:26:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eba24b8d9ac6984283729da7f78b42703cefa642","tid":1076390,"uid":235021,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T21:46:20.000Z","msg":"港喱：鬼佬民主好亂，嘈嘈閉閉，都係李光耀模式統治啱我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/l